# HOME DIRECTORY GIT: Ignore everything, whitelist only tracked paths
# This repo root is ~ (home). Only Documents/Personal/CLT/ is tracked.
*

# Whitelist the CLT tree (negation rules)
!Documents/
!Documents/Personal/
!Documents/Personal/CLT/
!Documents/Personal/CLT/**

# Within CLT, ignore generated/ephemeral content
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/.DS_Store
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/node_modules/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/*.tar.gz
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/logs/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/.goalie/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/.claude/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/.agentic-qe/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/.variants/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/00-DASHBOARD/backups/
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/00-DASHBOARD/WSJF-LIVE-2*.html
Documents/Personal/CLT/**/__pycache__/

# Keep .gitignore itself tracked
!.gitignore
